title: Cucuiș
data: The Cucuiș is a right tributary of the river Sibișel in Romania.[1][2] It flows into the Sibișel near Căstău.[3] Its length is 13 km (8.1 mi) and its basin size is 28 km2 (11 sq mi).[2] This article related to  a river in Hunedoara County is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it.
